<i>Our current polls do show,</i>
<i>among Republicans,,</i>

12:30.876 --> 12:33.173
<i>30% favor Trump...</i>
Liz.

12:33.208 --> 12:34.574
NEWSCASTER 3:
<i>...senator Ted Cruz,</i>

12:34.610 --> 12:38.112
<i>17% would vote</i>
<i>for Florida senator</i>
<i>Marco Rubio,</i>

12:38.147 --> 12:40.950
<i>and 5% for Ohio governor</i>
<i>John Kasich.</i>

12:40.985 --> 12:42.251
Liz.

