26:27.470 --> 26:28.711
MAN: Gambino's!

26:29.472 --> 26:30.779
Yeah, you can, um...

26:31.914 --> 26:33.342
I put a $20 in the mailbox.

26:34.818 --> 26:35.850
MAN: Sure.

26:39.449 --> 26:41.922
You can just leave it
on the...

26:41.957 --> 26:44.188
MAN: Yeah, I, uh...
I remember.

26:46.324 --> 26:47.664
Everything okay in there?

26:52.297 --> 26:53.296
Yeah.

26:55.102 --> 26:56.134
MAN: You sure?

26:56.939 --> 26:57.938
Yeah.

26:58.809 --> 26:59.841
I'm fine.

27:02.274 --> 27:03.273
Thank you.

27:05.244 --> 27:06.243
(METAL CLACKS)

27:07.114 --> 27:08.718
(FOOTSTEPS)

27:12.020 --> 27:13.118
(CHUCKLES LIGHTLY)

27:20.358 --> 27:21.797
