a relationship

27:56.966 --> 27:58.196
between your brain
and your body.

27:58.231 --> 27:59.769
If you know
how to make yourself calm,

27:59.804 --> 28:00.935
then your blood
pressure will...

28:00.970 --> 28:03.036
